<section id="faq-page-area" class="section-padding ">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- FAQ Content Start -->
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="faq-details-content">
                    <!-- Single FAQ Subject  Start -->
                    <div class="single-faq-sub">
                        <h3>Payment</h3>
                        <div class="single-faq-sub-content">
                            <div id="accordion">
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                                <span>If I make a reservation at this site, when will I get charged?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            A&S Car Rental currently offers two (2) methods of confirming a reservation. We offer a "Reserve Free Cancellation" option in which you pay at the time of making the reservation but you can receive a refund if you cancel 24 hours prior to your scheduled arrival. We also offer a "Reserve Pay On Arrival" option. This allows you to book a vehicle without prepaying at the time of making your reservation.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                                <span>If I return the vehicle early, will I receive a refund?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            In most cases, if you return a vehicle early, we will recalculate the rate and charge you according to the length of time you had the vehicle. However, some locations do charge an early return fee. You will need to review the location's policies to confirm.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                                <span>What forms of payment does A&S Car Rental accept?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            Each of our locations are independently owned and operated, you will need to review the location's policies to review the forms of payment it will accept. In addition some locations do have a specific policy for local renters.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Single FAQ Subject End -->
                    <!-- Single FAQ Subject  Start -->
                    <div class="single-faq-sub">
                        <h3>Preparation</h3>
                        <div class="single-faq-sub-content">
                            <div id="accordion_2">
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="heading4">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
                                                <span>What do I need to rent a vehicle from A&S Car Rental?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="collapse4" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading4" data-parent="#accordion_2">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            All drivers must possess a valid drivers license issued in their country of residence, and an acceptable means of payment as identified in the Location Policies.

                                            Some locations have additional requirements and restrictions, please check the Location Policies for your specific rental location.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                                <span>If my plans change after I have reserved a car, can I modify an existing reservation?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordion_2">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            To change an existing reservation you will need to either contact ACE Rent A Car for assistance or cancel your original reservation and rebook a new reservation. Please note that a new rental rate may apply when changes are made.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ Start -->
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                                <span>What insurance does A&S Car Rental offer?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordion_2">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            The renter is responsible for any damage to the vehicle or liability that occurs during the rental period. ACE locations offer Collision Damage Waiver and Supplemental Liability Insurance that release you from that responsibility. Your personal car insurance, homeowners' policy, or credit card supplements may provide some coverage. Please check with your insurance agent before your travel date.

                                            If you incur damages or liability not covered by your insurance, you will be personally responsible for those costs.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" id="headingSix">
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                                                <span>What is the minimum age for a renter?</span>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                                                <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseSix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix" data-parent="#accordion_2">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            All A&S Car Rental locations rent to drivers at least 25 years of age. If under the age of 25, please refer to the location's policy. Fees and vehicle restrictions may apply.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Single FAQ End -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
